            "title": "美股日誌｜ 2月動盪收官　銀行股崩盤　納指全月下跌3.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 2月動盪收官 銀行股崩盤 納指全月下跌3.3% \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OOwl2VZ_Mv.eZlUvRb86tg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/b35c35b0-142b-11f1-bbb2-dc73b834b056\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 2月動盪收官 銀行股崩盤 納指全月下跌3.3% </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周五下挫，道指領跌下跌逾1%，即超過 500 點。納指下跌0.8%，標普500指數下跌 0.4%，延續科技股此前急挫後的疲弱走勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指2月份僅錄得微升0.17%，勉強維持連續九個月上升的紀錄；納指及標普 500 指數本月則分別下跌逾3.3%及0.86%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受中東緊張局勢影響，油價及金價皆急升，油價收報67.29美元一桶，升2.08美元或3.19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8deb7320-21ec-4a18-ad61-38589a2da3c7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月27日（星期五）市况</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌521.28.05點或1.05%，報48,977.92點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌29.98點或0.43%，報6,878.88點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌210.17點或0.92%，報22,667.21點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報67.29美元一桶，升2.08美元或3.19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,296.4美元一盎司，升102美元或1.97%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報65,590.06美元，跌1,785.61美元或2.65%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報3.962厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國勞工統計局周五公布，1月份生產者價格指數(PPI)上漲0.5%，高於0.3%的預測，比上月多出0.1個百分點。 剔除波動較大的食品和能源價格的核心PPI經季節調整後上升0.8%，高於12月份的0.6%增幅，遠超預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業消息方面，該串流媒體巨頭<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Netflix;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NFLX/\">Netflix</a>放棄收購 Warner Bros. Discovery 的計劃，此舉令 Paramount Skydance 成功達成對該荷里活片廠的收購。雖然收購失敗，但市場認為是好事，股價收市升逾13%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國抵押貸款融資公司Market Financial Solutions(MFS)進入破產程序，市場擔心MFS倒閉，可能會對銀行股造成損失，多間銀行股受壓。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:富瑞;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JEF/\">富瑞</a>(JEF.US)跌高達9.3%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MS/\">摩根士丹利</a>(MS.US)挫6.2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美銀;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BAC/\">美銀</a>(BAC.US)、巴克萊銀行(BCS.US)跌約4%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:富國銀行;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/WFC/\">富國銀行</a>(WFC.US)跌5.6%，拖累道指今日大跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI周五宣布完成1,100億美元融資，未計入本輪集資資金估值達7,300億美元。 公司表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>於本輪融資中投資500億美元；軟銀及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">英偉達</a>(NVDA.US)則各投資300億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息指，SpaceX考慮最快3月保密提交IPO文件。這家由億萬富豪馬斯克創立的火箭和衛星公司，正推進史上最大規模的上市計畫，有望在6月掛牌上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:16;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:巴郡;cpos:16;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BRK-B/\">巴郡</a>新行政總裁 Greg Abel 預計將於周六發表其接替 Warren Buffett 後的首封年度致股東信，並將與該集團的季度及 2025 年業務更新一併公布。</p></div>",
